sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Mobile as Codex Mobile
    participant Bridge as Bridge API
    participant Files as Workspace Files
    participant MCP as Diagram MCP

    User->>Mobile: Open Diagrams section
    Mobile->>Bridge: GET /sdd/project/diagrams
    Bridge->>Files: Read Mermaid and SVG diagram artifacts
    Files-->>Bridge: Diagram content and metadata
    Bridge-->>Mobile: Diagram list
    User->>Mobile: Open SVG diagram
    Mobile->>Mobile: Render SVG with pan and zoom
    User->>Mobile: Request update
    Mobile->>Bridge: Start Codex run with MCP server selected
    Bridge->>MCP: Generate or update DiagramSpec/SVG
    MCP->>Files: Persist rendered artifact and metadata

